Company Overview of CNX Gas Company LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
CNX Gas Company LLC produces, markets, and sells coal bed methane and gas. The company produces and distributes pipeline natural gas. It also offers drilling services. The company was incorporated in 2001 and is based in Waynesburg, Pennsylvania. CNX Gas Company LLC operates as a subsidiary of CONSOL Energy Inc.


