CNX Gas Corp.







CNX Gas Corporation is an independent oil and gas corporation with headquarters in Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania. CNX Gas operates primarily in the Illinois and Appalachian basin regions, but has operations in Virginia, southwestern Pennsylvania, and northern Tennessee. CNX Gas is listed on the NYSE as CXG.  The company was founded in 2005 as an offshoot of CONSOL Energy Inc.
Contact Information for Royalty Owners – Tel. (724) 485-4000
Those who own gas royalties and oil royalties are an important group to CNX Gas Corp. If you receive oil royalty or gas royalty from a lease under production by CNX Gas Corp., you   can contact them at (724) 485-4000.
CNX Gas Production Volume Verification
If you are a lease holder (lessor) currently under production by CNX Gas Corp.,   you can verify your oil and gas production  volumes by  visiting How      to Verify Your Oil and Gas Production Volumes. This page   includes    links to the state agencies that record oil and gas   production data  and   also covers the basics of how oil and gas is   measured.
Cash Payment for Your Royalty
If you own a producing royalty you can receive a no obligation cash offer for your producing royalties from the MineralWeb experts.








